ZH: 这个导火索能引爆整个炸弹。
EN: This fuse can detonate the entire bomb.

ZH: 他们找到了导火索并立即将它切断。
EN: They found the fuse and immediately cut it off.

ZH: 这根导火索已经被点燃，我们必须赶快远离。
EN: This fuse has been lit, we must quickly move away.

ZH: 导火索已经点燃，我们只能祈祷炸弹不会爆炸。
EN: The fuse has been lit, we can only pray the bomb doesn't explode.

ZH: 他迅速拿起了导火索将它扔向敌人。
EN: He quickly picked up the fuse and threw it towards the enemy.

ZH: 这个导火索看起来很脆弱，我们需要小心处理。
EN: This fuse looks fragile, we need to handle it carefully.

ZH: 导火索已经被撕开，我们必须找到替代方案。
EN: The fuse has been torn apart, we must find an alternative solution.

ZH: 不要拿玩导火索，这是很危险的。
EN: Don't play with the fuse, it's very dangerous.

ZH: 听说敌军已经损坏了我们的导火索。
EN: I heard that the enemy has damaged our fuse.

ZH: 导火索被沾湿了，我们需要找到更快的引爆方式。
EN: The fuse got wet, we need to find a quicker way to detonate.

ZH: 把导火索重新包裹并妥善存放。
EN: Re-wrap the fuse and store it properly.

ZH: 只有导火索被引爆才会触发炸弹。
EN: Only when the fuse is ignited will the bomb be triggered.

ZH: 导火索的长度决定了炸弹的爆炸时间。
EN: The length of the fuse determines the explosion time of the bomb.

ZH: 这个导火索因为过期已经不可用了。
EN: This fuse is no longer usable due to expiration.

ZH: 导火索被误用，结果导致爆炸。
EN: The fuse was misused, resulting in an explosion.

ZH: 敌人似乎知道我们的导火索的位置。
EN: The enemy seems to know the location of our fuse.

ZH: 导火索已经被固定在炸弹上。
EN: The fuse has been securely attached to the bomb.

ZH: 没有正确的引爆导火索，炸弹不会爆炸。
EN: Without properly igniting the fuse, the bomb won't explode.

ZH: 导火索已被启用，炸弹随时可能爆炸。
EN: The fuse has been activated, the bomb could explode at any moment.

ZH: 炸弹的导火索在几秒钟内就会燃烧完毕。
EN: The bomb's fuse will burn out in a few seconds.
